<th align=center>
Too many emperors of the arts have been walking around for too long without any clothes on.  It's time somebody said so.<br><br>And a few paupers of the arts have been walking around in silks and ermines.  It's time somebody said that, too.<br><br>The <a href="gallery1.html">&quot;Gallery&quot;</a> pages are intended only as another sort of table of contents.  If you do use them - and I wouldn't bother - hit "Comments" below the thumbnails to see the point of it all.</th></tr></table>

