  <div class="post"><a name="612453595348477822"></a>
         
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 
	 Lisa Hoffman and Natasha Rose Chenier Live at Zeke's Gallery Volume 264
	 
    </h3>
    

	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      Howdy!<br /><br />Lisa Hoffman and Natasha Rose Chenier played here last night. Natasha Rose Chenier played her three songs first (Letter from the Future, Heart and Thunder (version one) and Heart and Thunder (version two)) and then Lisa Hoffman played Losing Streak, More the Same, Friend of Mine, Came to Stay, Your Disease, Passing Through, The Real Slim Shady, and These Houses.<br /><br />If you would like to hear it, <a href="http://www.archive.org/download/Lisa_Hoffman_Vol_264/Lisa_vbr.mp3">click here</a> [<span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;font-size:85%;" >84.4 MB, 54:12 minutes</span>] <a href="http://www.archive.org/download/Lisa_Hoffman_Vol_264/Lisa_Hoffman_Vol_264_vbr.m3u">stream</a>, <a href="http://www.archive.org/download/Lisa_Hoffman_Vol_264/Lisa.flac">flac</a>, <a href="http://www.archive.org/download/Lisa_Hoffman_Vol_264/Lisa.ogg">ogg vorbis</a>.
    </div>
    </div>

