    <h3 class="post-title">
	 
	 Internet news on the Biennale
	 
    </h3>
    

	         <div class="post-body">
	<div>
      Howdy!<br /><br />Submitted without comment<blockquote style="font-style: italic;"><ol><span style="font-size:85%;"><li><a href="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/LAC.20070521.MONTREAL21/TPStory/Entertainment">Sarah Milroy's review in the Globe & Mail</a></li><li><a href="http://www.voir.ca/artsvisuels/artsvisuels.aspx?iIDArticle=51496">Nathalie Guimond of Voir reviews the David Altmejd exhibit</a></li><li><a href="http://www.ledevoir.com/2007/05/26/144871.html">RenÃ© Viau of Le Devoir reviews the David Altmejd exhibit</a></li></span><span style="font-size:85%;"><li><a href="http://www.montrealmirror.com/2007/051007/music3.html">Rupert Bottenberg of the Mirror on the Music</a></li></span><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://www.montrealmirror.com/2007/051007/visualarts.html">Christine Redfern of the Mirror on the art and the music</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://www.hour.ca/visualarts/visualarts.aspx?iIDArticle=12017">Susannah Wesley of the Hour on David Altmejd</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://www.voir.ca/musique/musique.aspx?iIDArticle=51321">StÃ©phane Martel of Voir on Peaches</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20070510/CPARTS/705100873/1017/CPARTS">Mario Cloutier of La Presse on the art</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://montreal.24heures.ca/ArtsEtSpectacles/2007/05/09/4164755-sun.html">Louise Dussault of 24 heures on the music</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://fugues.vortex.qc.ca/main.cfm?p=100&amp;Article_ID=9107">Denis-Daniel BoullÃ© of Fuges on the art</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://www.canoe.com/divertissement/arts-scene/nouvelles/2007/05/05/4156463-jdm.html">Marilou SÃ©guin of the Journal de Montreal on the music and the art</a></span></li><li><span style="font-size:85%;"><a href="http://www.radio-canada.ca/arts-spectacl